title: S_U_P_R_E_M_A_C_Y
overview: Two Special Agents, Lilith and Kerry race are tasked with finding a hidden facility holding a project simply known as S_U_P_R_E_M_A_C_Y which they fear may be a plan to destroy the world. However, they quickly become in jeopardy when they are ambushed by a group of Unknown Masked Attackers who threaten their mission, their lives... And the world.
